flowchart TB
  contributor["Contributor or agent"]:::person
  reviewer["Reviewer or maintainer"]:::person
  execution["Local shell and GitHub Actions<br/>[Validation execution]"]:::external
  adapter_user["Codex, Claude Code, and opencode user"]:::person

  subgraph repo["RigorLoop repository<br/>[Git repository]"]
    governance["Governance and workflow guidance<br/>[Markdown]"]:::container
    lifecycle["Lifecycle artifacts<br/>[Markdown and YAML]"]:::container
    architecture["Canonical architecture package<br/>[Markdown and Mermaid]"]:::container
    changes["Change-local evidence<br/>[Markdown and YAML]"]:::container
    templates["Templates and diagram styles<br/>[Markdown and Mermaid]"]:::container
    skills["Canonical skills and adapter templates<br/>[Markdown and templates]"]:::container
    scripts["Validation and generation scripts<br/>[Python and shell]"]:::container
    generated["Generated runtime mirrors and adapters<br/>[Generated Markdown, YAML, and command files]"]:::container
    release["Release evidence<br/>[YAML, Markdown, smoke evidence]"]:::container
    legacy["Legacy architecture archive<br/>[Archived Markdown]"]:::container
  end

  contributor -->|authors and updates| lifecycle
  contributor -->|uses scaffolds from| templates
  contributor -->|edits canonical sources in| skills
  reviewer -->|reviews C4, arc42, ADRs, and evidence in| architecture
  reviewer -->|reviews lifecycle state and closeout in| changes
  governance -->|defines routing and source-of-truth rules for| lifecycle
  governance -->|declares authored/generated boundaries for| skills
  lifecycle -->|requires current architecture truth from| architecture
  changes -->|merge durable architecture content back into| architecture
  changes -->|record durable decisions as ADRs in| lifecycle
  templates -->|scaffold architecture and ADR records in| lifecycle
  skills -->|are transformed by| scripts
  scripts -->|refresh| generated
  scripts -->|validate lifecycle, metadata, review artifacts, release data, and drift for| lifecycle
  scripts -->|run in| execution
  release -->|describes publication of| generated
  generated -->|is consumed by| adapter_user
  legacy -->|preserves historical evidence after merge-back to| architecture
  architecture -->|summarizes and links ADRs in| lifecycle

